{"tid":1313502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[沙田]被遺忘的行山路線- 道風山!!!!!","createTime":"2019-07-13T19:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T06:53:32.000Z","uid":42194,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea578b87d38fec0cd50b8fe5fd2698918e15aa3d","tid":1313502,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:35:55.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打<br />\n今日我想向大家介紹一條被遺忘O既行山路線<br />\n係由沙田火車站巴士站行過去大圍O既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n步程大約30分鐘<br />\n非常適合一家大細郊遊之用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得新城市太多人? <span style=\"color: red;\">此路不通?</span> 想去D 人少D O既地方?<br />\n一於行下道風山啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路線如下:<br />\n1. 起點係排頭村, 村公所果個位置附近, 有條小斜路上斜, 大概可容納2人並排行山, 2邊好多村屋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i9tuxLz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi9tuxLz.png&h=c2d5d775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NogzJSf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNogzJSf.png&h=1f06ddca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 可以沿住呢條小路上, 約10 分鐘就可以上到道風山個小迴旋處啦 (紅圈位置)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xg9hGEm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXg9hGEm.png&h=8feb2178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4q1oTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4q1oTm.png&h=a541e03f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n3. 拿, 黎到呢度就好玩啦, 呢個行山路線都有幾條, 幾多變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n紅圈位置係大家身處O既位置, 就咁睇都最少有2條路線去大圍<br />\n路線1去大圍火車站附近O既鬧市區<br />\n路線2係去美林<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZBcvyJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZBcvyJ.png&h=d488f32f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我以去大圍火車站作終點去計, 大約半個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47XK57N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47XK57N.png&h=d7d01aff&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 當然, 大家梗係唔好忘記, 行完山個身好臭, 記得換返件衫先好上車返屋企啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行山路線分享完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f70e272f6010f0e96aa71dc3874a2ee37447b7","tid":1313502,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:36:10.000Z","msg":"推到大家睇到"},{"pid":"9db45829492da20a2e371dc3f2563343fba8dbe1","tid":1313502,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:37:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f2e06d9574da968a324bdf159dc3c6523f4f886","tid":1313502,"uid":199223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:40:32.000Z","msg":"山路需可退，但一樣易封易包抄。<br />\n<br />\n無惡意，但行山要安全為主，似乎未必合適<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e91f119a5fe23ebbcff36d57665795f8d00675d","tid":1313502,"uid":199223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f2e06d9574da968a324bdf159dc3c6523f4f886","tid":1313502,"uid":199223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:40:32.000Z","msg":"山路需可退，但一樣易封易包抄。<br />\n<br />\n無惡意，但行山要安全為主，似乎未必合適<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:41:55.000Z","msg":"O處最高危"},{"pid":"180e8e18118cd235dcd1609ad06221aa1ceb864e","tid":1313502,"uid":224528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:46:14.000Z","msg":"行山要知道自己行緊咩山 起點終點係乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8e029dee6dc0a5fab1de92b6287d8bc6498cfe","tid":1313502,"uid":42194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f2e06d9574da968a324bdf159dc3c6523f4f886","tid":1313502,"uid":199223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:40:32.000Z","msg":"山路需可退，但一樣易封易包抄。<br />\n<br />\n無惡意，但行山要安全為主，似乎未必合適<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTi